  "id": 5080980370096128,
  "name": "Support path() and shape() in shape-outside",
  "summary": "Adds support for the path() and shape() shape functions in the CSS shape-outside property. These functions allow developers to define the shape of `shape-outside` more flexibly and support animation.\n\nDemo:\n- https://codepen.io/una/full/ogzRBWV\n- https://codepen.io/yisi/full/EaNjzvR",
